Requirements:

	Android(> 2.2,froyo)

Installation & Usage guidelines:

	1:Download the alipi.apk file from this link hhttps://play.google.com/store/search?q=alipi&c=apps

	2:Click on the alipi.apk follow the instructions to install the application

	3:Start the application and enter any url which has re-narration(example:a11y.in/a11y_dw/). 
	
	4:After the web-page loads,press the rennaration button in the action bar(at the top) after it turns green.

	5:choose the language or blog and then The web-page loads with the re-narrated content.

	6:If audio is present, a audio button appears next to the rennaratibon button. Click on it to choose and listen to the audio